---
layout: base.njk
title: Shelters & Services
description: "Florida shelters, humane societies, SPCAs, and county animal services that may have rabbits available for adoption."
value_index: 5
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <h1>Shelters, Humane Societies & County Services</h1>
  <p>{{ directory.shelters_and_services | length }} Florida shelters and government animal services that may have rabbits available.</p>
  {% set v = directory.shared_values.values[value_index] %}<p class="hero-epigraph"><a href="/values/#{{ v.statement | slugify }}">{{ v.statement }}</a></p>
</section>

<div class="shelters-intro">
  <p>The following shelters and government animal services may have rabbits available for adoption. Contact them directly to ask about rabbit availability. For rabbit-focused rescue organizations, see the <a href="/directory/">main directory</a>.</p>
</div>

<div class="shelters-list">
  {%- for group in directory.shelters_and_services | groupByRegion %}
  <div class="region-group">
    <h2 class="region-heading" id="{{ group.region | slugify }}">{{ group.region }}</h2>
    <div class="shelter-rows">
      {%- for shelter in group.shelters %}
      <a class="shelter-row" href="{{ shelter.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span class="shelter-name">{{ shelter.name }}</span>
        <span class="shelter-arrow">↗</span>
      </a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
  {%- endfor %}
</div>

<div class="shelters-footer">
  <div class="correction-cta">
    <p>Is your organization missing or incorrect?</p>
    <a class="btn-primary" href="/contact/">Submit a Correction &#8594;</a>
  </div>
</div>
